      • searchPartValue

        public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<Part> searchPartValue​(java.lang.String search)
        Populates Parts table in Modify Product form with parts that have part names that match the value entered into search bar in Modify Product form. If no matches are found, allParts is displayed.
        Parameters:
        search - Value entered into search bar in Modify Product form
        Returns:
        Parts with matching part names to entered value, or all parts if no matches are found

      • partMatchSearch

        public static boolean partMatchSearch​(java.lang.String search)

        Parameters:
